com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce

Annotation Type BigQueryDataField


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface BigQueryDataField
    Annotation to provide additional information related to BigQuery data fields. @see TableFieldSchema.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.String description
      Description of the BigQuery field
      BigQueryFieldMode mode
      Mode of a bigquery table column determines whether it is repeated, required or nullable.
      java.lang.String name
      The name of the bigquery column.

    • Element Detail

      • description

        public abstract java.lang.String description
        Description of the BigQuery field
        Default:
        ""

      • name

        public abstract java.lang.String name
        The name of the bigquery column. By default it is same as the name of the field in the class. Use this annotation to provide a different name.
        Default:
        ""

      • mode

        public abstract BigQueryFieldMode mode
        Mode of a bigquery table column determines whether it is repeated, required or nullable. A required column must not be left null or empty which loading data. By default it is nullable.
        Default:
        com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.BigQueryFieldMode.NULLABLE
